com.interpss.dc.pv.inverter

Interface AbstractDcAcInverter

  • All Superinterfaces:
    com.hazelcast.nio.serialization.DataSerializable, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, IDcAcInverter, NameTag, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    DcAcInverter
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractDcAcInverterImpl, DcAcInverterImpl

    public interface AbstractDcAcInverter
extends NameTag, IDcAcInverter
    A representation of the model object 'Abstract Dc Ac Inverter'. For DcAcInverter extention implementation. You should extend AbstractDcAcInverter and implement the IDcAcInverter interface.

    The following features are supported:

    • Pv Dc Bus
    See Also:
    DcAcInverterPackage.getAbstractDcAcInverter()

        PVDcBus getPvDcBus()
